* [Installing <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> on AWS](https://docs.pivotal.io/tkgi/installing-aws.html).
* [Installing and Configuring TAS for VMs on Windows](https://docs.pivotal.io/application-service/2-8/windows/installing.html)
